> Entertainment Jimmy Fallon falls again, hurts fingers on other hand FILE - In this Aug. 25, 2014, file photo, Jimmy Fallon presents an award at the 66th Annual Primetime Emmy Awards in Los Angeles. Fallon got the royal treatment at Harvard. "The Tonight Show" host and "Saturday Night Live" alum was honored Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015, by the Harvard Lampoon. Four months Fallon needed emergency surgery to save one of his fingers after falling in his kitchen, Fallon hurt his other hand in spill at a party in his honor on Saturday. (Photo by Chris Pizzello/Invision/AP, File) 
